    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight">When should a small business hire an internet marketing consultant?</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">An internet marketing consultant helps you decide what to fix first, where to spend your budget, and how SEO marketing, ads, content, and your website should work together.</p>
